<p>On Thursday, President Trump warned Hamas that if killings in Gaza continue, &quot;we will have no choice but to go in and kill them&quot; [straitstimes.com#1][scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#2][euronews.com#1]. He later clarified that the United States would not send its own forces into Gaza, saying &quot;It&#x27;s not going to be us&quot; [nytimes.com#1][scmp.com#1]. The remarks come a week after a ceasefire and hostage deal took effect in the two-year war between Israel and Hamas, even as reports noted internal violence persisting in the territory—an uneasy backdrop that also underscores some progress toward reduced hostilities [scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#2][euronews.com#1].</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/GqkQ0WalvFVITW39T6LvlGVSgzSBuXAR0kbU2i7cMXNoN5ML4RGErjQxBWHOKMbhGgeYgUE6t0mPeLihRyiSP8QpT_4jCwFYrgl35uU3pANu1flRI0Es58J4vbZG2Yvt5jt7z8BN7s7w4PELeMASRQzJrvSHNIH47x3QZMe5jkiKSecB3XvJL2evEing56037PD-nWHCsAY' alt='Hamas militants stood guard on Wednesday as the Red Cross transported bodies of hostages who died in Gaza.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Tone shift: Before issuing the threat, Trump had previously downplayed internal violence in Gaza since the recent truce, marking a sharper turn in rhetoric [scmp.com#1][thehindu.com#2][euronews.com#1].</li><li>Media framing: The Straits Times characterized his initial wording as opening the door to direct US military action in Gaza [straitstimes.com#1].</li><li>Conflict duration: Coverage described the Israel–Hamas fighting as a two-year war preceding the latest ceasefire and hostage deal [scmp.com#1].</li><li>Humanitarian detail: On Wednesday, Hamas militants stood guard as the International Committee of the Red Cross transported the bodies of hostages who died in Gaza [nytimes.com#1].</li></ul><blockquote>We will have no choice but to go in and kill them - President Donald Trump</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>President Trump: Warned of severe consequences for Hamas over ongoing killings in Gaza, then clarified the US would not send troops. (<a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/middle-east/article/3329305/trump-threatens-go-and-kill-hamas-if-gaza-killings-continue'>South China Morning Post</a>)</li><li>Media assessment: The Straits Times suggested the initial comments signaled potential for direct US military action in Gaza. (<a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/trump-says-if-hamas-keeps-killing-no-choice-but-to-go-in'>The Straits Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/united-states/trump-says-if-hamas-keeps-killing-no-choice-but-to-go-in'>Trump threatens to ‘go in and kill’ Hamas if it doesn’t stop Gaza killings</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.scmp.com/news/world/middle-east/article/3329305/trump-threatens-go-and-kill-hamas-if-gaza-killings-continue'>Trump threatens to ‘go in and kill’ Hamas if Gaza bloodshed continues</a> - scmp.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/shorts/watch-trump-warns-hamas-if-they-dont-behave-well-take-care-of-it/article70174251.ece'>Watch: Trump warns Hamas: ‘If they don’t behave, we’ll take care of it’</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2025/10/17/trump-threatens-hamas-with-military-action-if-bloodshed-persists-in-gaza'>Trump threatens Hamas with military action if group&#x27;s bloodshed in Gaza persists</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/16/us/politics/trump-hamas-warnings-gaza-strikes.html'>Trump Warns Hamas of Strikes if Violence in Gaza Continues</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.reddit.com/r/worldnews/comments/1o8oh1e/trump_if_hamas_doesnt_stop_killing_gazans_we_will/'>Trump: If Hamas doesn’t stop killing Gazans, ‘we will have no choice but to go in and kill them’</a> - reddit.com</li></ul>